---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | Love Your Words">
  <style>
    .legal-page {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 70px 6% 90px;
    }
    .legal-page h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }
    .effective {
      color: rgba(28,24,48,0.55);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .legal-page h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 36px 0 12px;
      color: #1C1830;
      font-family: 'Outfit', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }
    .legal-page p {
      font-size: 1.0325rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .legal-page a { color: #7B52C8; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>

  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="effective">Effective July 3, 2026</div>

    <h2>Welcome</h2>
    <p>These terms cover your use of loveyourwords.com, the website of Love Your Words, the copywriting practice of Diane Anderson. Using the site means you accept these terms.</p>

    <h2>What this site is for</h2>
    <p>The site describes copywriting and content services and shares writing on related topics. Everything here is offered for general information. It is not legal, financial, or professional advice.</p>

    <h2>Ownership of content</h2>
    <p>The writing, images, and design on this site belong to Diane Anderson unless credited otherwise. You are welcome to link to any page. Reusing or republishing content requires written permission first: <a href="mailto:hello@loveyourwords.com">hello@loveyourwords.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>Working together</h2>
    <p>Descriptions of services on this site are invitations to start a conversation. Actual client engagements, including scope, fees, timelines, and deliverables, get agreed in writing separately. Nothing on this site by itself creates a client relationship.</p>

    <h2>Outside links and tools</h2>
    <p>Some pages link to or embed outside services, such as the Calendly scheduling calendar. Those services belong to their own companies and run under their own terms and policies.</p>

    <h2>Plain-language liability</h2>
    <p>This site is provided as is. Reasonable care goes into keeping it accurate and available, and even so, no guarantee is made that every page is error-free or always online. To the fullest extent the law allows, Love Your Words is not liable for damages arising from use of this site.</p>

    <h2>Governing law</h2>
    <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of California.</p>

    <h2>Questions</h2>
    <p>Write to <a href="mailto:hello@loveyourwords.com">hello@loveyourwords.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
